title: 2019 CFB Week 13 Slate
description:
El Pres, Big Cat and Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. As the podcast is collectively climbing back to .500, the whole room defends there allegiances to whether they are Rico Ryders or part of the Wolf Pack and Rico will not stand for liars who falsely accuse him of picks he didn't make!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
